{
  "stem": "7598.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, eventually, at the beginning of May one day we-- we got onto the plane and we arrived in Bristol.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bumpy and we landed on the sea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't remember much about seaplanes, but my husband seems to know that they were very much the in thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were mainly army personnel of all sorts of nationality.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got to Bristol and there we were welcomed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we were interrogated by the Army, the Navy-- what is it?-- the Air Force, and the Intelligence.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were extremely knowledgeable and extremely kind to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew everything about us, but they just wanted to make sure that we were my parents' children and we were refugees-- after all, my brother was 17-- and that we weren't spies.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were shown maps of the airport in Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were asked to tell them what we knew about it, whether we knew that it had been enlarged or not.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, they were obviously quite satisfied that we were who we were after a long time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the intelligent man turned around and said, you can go home to your parents now, but I'm afraid your brother has to come into an internment camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think everything was just too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was overawed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, I can't leave him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I haven't left him for two years and I don't speak the language.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at the time, it only seemed normal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But when I think there was a war on and this man said to me, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One of us will take you all the way to London, but I'm afraid your brother has to come for interrogations for a few days.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
